name: Egg Bash VR 2
summary: Embark on a wild adventure in "EggBashVR2" by CSVRStudios! Swing through treetops, solve challenging puzzles, and outsmart mischievous eggs in this action-packed VR experience. Whether you're a seasoned explorer or a newcomer to the jungle, EggBashVR2 promises endless fun for all ages. Ready to join the monkey world.
